<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idec022edf-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53" identifier="/us/usc/t51/s50923"><num value="50923">§ 50923.</num><heading> Report to Congress</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Transportation shall submit to Congress an annual report to accompany the President’s budget request that—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idec022ee0-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53" identifier="/us/usc/t51/s50923/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> describes all activities undertaken under this chapter, including a description of the process for the application for and approval of licenses under this chapter and recommendations for legislation that may further commercial launches and reentries; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idec022ee1-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53" identifier="/us/usc/t51/s50923/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> reviews the performance of the regulatory activities and the effectiveness of the Office of Commercial Space Transportation.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idec022ee2-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/105/303/tI/s102/a/16">Pub. L. 105–303, title I, § 102(a)(16)</ref>, <date date="1998-10-28">Oct. 28, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2851">112 Stat. 2851</ref>, <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s70121">§ 70121 of title 49</ref>; renumbered § 70121 then <ref href="/us/usc/t51/s50923">§ 50923 of title 51</ref>, <ref href="/us/pl/111/314/s4/d/2">Pub. L. 111–314, § 4(d)(2)</ref>, (3)(W), <date date="2010-12-18">Dec. 18, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3440">124 Stat. 3440</ref>, 3441.)</sourceCredit>
